# 陕西·西安
Xi’an, Shaanxi

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,980
# 我坐在板凳上看人家吃面条
I’m sitting on a wooden bench and watching them eating noodles

3
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:08,600
# 每个人都是抱着一个不锈钢的盆
Everyone is holding a stainless steel pot

4
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:13,600
# 眼睁睁地看着他们 吃完了一整盆的面条
And they finished whole pots of noodles while I could only watch

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:16,400
# 这陕西十大怪当中的碗盆难分开
It’s called “Bowls as big as basins” in Shaanxi Ten strange customs

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,560
# 我今天算是见识到了
I saw it today

7
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:21,080
# 在陕西 尤其是关中地区
In Shaanxi, expecilly the Guanzhong area

8
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,080
# 面食的吃法是多种多样
There are so many ways to eat wheaten food

9
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:25,600
# 如果你和我一样 来这边走一遭
If you come here like me

10
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,120
# 怕是顿顿也不带重样的
It's hard to have even one repeated meal

11
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:44,160
# 蘸水面
Zhanshui noodle

12
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,920
# 我要了一个裤带蘸水面
I ordered a belt zhanshui noodle

13
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:53,000
# 阿姨先端来了一个小碗
The auntie brought a small bowl first

14
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,960
# 我说 不应该是面条像裤带吗 怎么碗这么小
I was like, shouldn't the noodles be as wide as a belt? How come the bowl is so small?

15
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:58,400
# 放近了一看才发现
I took a closer look and found out

16
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:00,080
# 这个只是蘸水
This is just the dipping sauce

17
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:03,640
# 真正的面条在这里 用盆装的
The noodles are actually in this pot

18
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:06,520
# 面条真的是像裤带一样
The noodles really look like a belts

19
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,480
# 又宽 又粗
Wide and thick

20
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:11,200
# 关键这一盆才12块钱
And this pot of noodles only costs 12 yuan

21
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:17,120
# 别的地方加面条都是再加一些
In other places, we add noodles by orders

22
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:21,160
# 这边面条是按根来加 一根3块钱
Here we add by strips. Each strip is 3 yuan

23
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:25,480
# 端上来的除了面条之外 还有蘸水
The noodles come with the dipping sauce

24
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,840
# 能够看到蘸水红油油的
We can see the dipping sauce is red and shiny

25
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:32,080
# 上面就是芝麻 辣子 香葱和蒜末
There are sesame, spicy pepper, green onion and mashed garlic on top

26
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:36,440
# 是西红柿卤子吧
Is that tomato marinade?

27
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:40,600
# 你看 咱们在这边吃面 他们一般都会先剥一瓣蒜
Usually we'll peel a garlic to go with the noodles

28
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,200
# 但是我看里面是有蒜汁的
But I saw they already added garlic sauce

29
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,800
# 咱们就不剥蒜了
So we can skip that

30
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:48,760
# 直接是把面条扯进蘸水里
Just drag the noodle into the dipping sauce

31
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:53,080
# 面条真的是又长又宽
The noodle is really long and thick

32
00:01:55,320 --> 00:02:00,600
# 我弄了老半天 这一根面条都没有到头
I haven't even got one noodle after this long

33
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,800
# 这才是一根面
This is just one strip of noodle

34
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:13,280
# 这一根面就顶普通的一碗面
The potion size of one strip can compare with an order of regular noodles

35
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,320
# 面条就像大面皮一样
Like “da mian pi”

36
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:29,360
# 蘸水真的是很有味
The dipping sauce is very delicious

37
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,920
# 里面有西红柿的酸甜感
With sour-sweetness from the tomatoes

38
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:35,280
# 还有芝麻和辣椒的香味
And the fragrance of sesame and chilis as well

39
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:38,840
# 蒜汁放在里面 一点不会觉得突兀
Garlic sauce in the dipping sauce doesn't abrupt at all

40
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:57,080
# 这一根面进去 盆里就像少了好多面条一样
It feels so much less in the pot after finishing one noodle

41
00:02:57,080 --> 00:03:02,280
# 平常的话 姑娘吃一根就差不多了 两根都有点撑了
Normally, one noodle should feed lady and two noodles will make her stuffed

42
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,600
# 男的 可以多加一根
Men can probably have one more

43
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:13,800
# 一根面条1两7
The weight of a noodle is about 1.7 liang (85 grams)

44
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:24,640
# 1两7x4根
Multiply by four

45
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:34,200
# 咱们都是按照我们当地人的饭量做的
The potion size is designed according to our local people

46
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:39,200
# 见过最多的人吃几根  最多的能吃16根
What is the record that one has eaten? 16 noodles

47
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,680
# 很胖吗
Is he fat?

48
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:44,000
# 不胖 个子还没他高
No, and the guy is even shorter than him

49
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,640
# 特别能吃 一来就是16根
He just eats a lot and ordered 16 noodles all at once

50
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:50,080
# 像南方人吃不完这一份
Southern guys cannot even finish one order

51
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:53,320
# 他们也就两根就吃撑了
Two noodles can make them stuffed

52
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:57,360
# 咱们当地人就是 基本上4根够吃
Our local people usually have four noodles

53
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,720
# 4根差不多
About four noodles

54
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,040
# 4根都吃饱了
They will get full after four noodles

55
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:03,000
# 在咱家吃面就是两怪
We can observe two among the ten strange customs in our restaurant

56
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:06,680
# 一个是 面条宽
First, noodles as wide as belts

57
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:09,320
# 另一个大老碗  碗盆分不开
Second, bowls as big as basins

58
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:12,200
# 12块钱一盆面
12 yuan for a pot of noodles

